{"tid":12963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「估地方」認識4年忍不了3個月，他上了小女友換牢飯","createTime":"2016-11-30T01:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T01:10:39.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fef5d5dec89db233b369b32e2712c8a51f15e32","tid":12963,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:06:46.000Z","msg":"2016年11月30日06:50      <br />\n<br />\n認識4年後交往，她差了3個月滿16歲，但他克制不住慾望高漲，換來6個月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，新北市鄭姓少年2011年間在教會結識1名少女，4年後交往，他18歲、少女當時15歲，差3個月滿16歲，精蟲衝腦時與少女發生關係，造成她懷孕還墮胎，新北地院依對14歲以上未滿16歲女子為性交罪，判鄭男6個月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161130/640_cb218b598ab5de76ad5de730342478f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161130%2F640_cb218b598ab5de76ad5de730342478f9.jpg&h=5d9d7408&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5f09a2721d5c6a1ed26ff52cefa31d3b15eae6d","tid":12963,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"只差一點點。。"},{"pid":"353e545915e6d9198d6f317e2ecc60c0b2b72a6f","tid":12963,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:10:39.000Z","msg":"新北加1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}